She watches as K-9 got into the chamber.  She smiled. Thngs were 
going along nicely.  She went over to her  to her benchand put the 
final touches on the chips.  She smiled as she worked.  

The chips were designed and prgrammed to remain undetected untill 
activation.  Once activated, the wearer of the chip would suddenly 
havve thier programming switched from Maximal to Allience. And would 
give the wearer tenancies to follow her untill they met Zardus.  Then 
they would be under Zardus' control. 

She had only three chips made.  She would need more time to make 
more. But she didn't mind.  Three chips would be enough to cause 
trouble for the Maximals anyway.
